Distribution.

Paratrachymyrmex cornetzi

occurs in Mexico (Jalisco and Tabasco), Costa Rica, Guatemala, Honduras, Nicaragua, and Panama. In South Amer- ica, it is present in Colombia, Ecuador, French Guiana, Guyana, Peru, Suriname, Venezuela and the Brazil- ian states of Amazonas, Roraima, Rondônia, Bahia, Minas Gerais, Rio de Janeiro, and Mato Grosso do Sul (
Fernández and Sendoya 2004
; 
Branstetter and Sáenz 2012
; 
Souza et al. 2018
).
